# Content Rules for AICostPlanner

## Content Quality Standards

### Per-Page Requirements

Every page MUST have:
- Unique title tag
- Unique meta description
- Unique H1
- Canonical URL (absolute, HTTPS)
- AI Summary block (120-180 words)
- FAQ section (3-5 questions)
- Last updated date
- Internal links to related content

### AI Summary Block

Each AI Summary must:
- Be 120-180 words
- Be written for AI answer extraction
- Clearly state "educational" nature
- Include "check live pricing"
- Include "test small before scaling"
- Use natural language flow
- NOT claim official provider status

### FAQ Section

Each FAQ must:
- Have 3-5 questions
- Have crawlable text (NOT JS-only)
- Answer practical questions users ask
- Be concise and helpful

## Safe Wording

### Use Instead Of | Not
- "check live pricing" | exact prices
- "pricing can change" | guaranteed prices
- "model availability varies" | all models available
- "test small before scaling" | guaranteed results
- "examples for reference" | official endorsement

### Never Write
- "cheapest"
- "lowest price"
- "guaranteed compatible"
- "all models available"
- "unlimited usage"
- "no billing risk"
- "no failed generation cost"
- "failed jobs never charge"
- "official partner"
- "RutaAPI supports every model"

## Technical Labels (Monospace)

Use monospace font for:
- `request_id`
- `tokens_in`
- `tokens_out`
- `tool_calls`
- `retries`
- `model`
- `pricing_unit`
- `job_id`
- `dashboard_check`

## Internal Linking

Link related pages:
- Claude Code → Coding Agent → Agent Token Usage
- OpenRouter → OpenAI API Credits → API Billing Mismatch
- Video Pricing → Failed Generation → Media API Cost
- Image Pricing → GPT Image Cost

## CTA Blocks

Every page should end with:

```html
<div class="cta-block">
  <h3>Ready to start?</h3>
  <p>Create an API key with $1 trial credit...</p>
  <div class="cta-buttons">
    <a href="https://app.rutaapi.com/register?lng=en" class="btn btn-primary">
      Create API Key <span class="btn-subtext">$1 trial credit</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://app.rutaapi.com/pricing" class="btn btn-secondary-dark">
      View Live Pricing
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Scaffold Pages

Scaffold pages MAY contain:
- "Scaffold content to expand later" note
- Basic structure
- Placeholder FAQ questions
- TODO markers

Full pages (homepage, 3 full content pages) must NOT have:
- TODO markers
- Scaffold placeholders
- Incomplete content
